		|	Ûfor_staticİ of (For_Static)
		|	Ûfor_tmarkİ of (For_Tmark)
		|	Ûexit_whenİ of (Exit_When)
		|	Ûexitİ
		|	Ûretİ of (Return)
		|	Ûproc_no_ivarsİ of (Proc_Call_No_Ivars);
